Exactly same as 01-matrix leetcode 542
Except in this question we also have walls that is cells we cannot traverse
Initialize distance grid with value -Infinity
Then fill all treasure cell distance grid elements as zero Because distance of treasure from treasure is of course zero
then run multisource BFS from all treasure cells if and only if the coordinates are feasible and distance element of that cell equals minus Infinity
then update the value of that distance cell
and because we have initialized the entire distance grid with minus Infinity value hence any land cell that is unreachable will remain minus Infinity
and we will get the correct answer as required
